item.title: Nabi's 12-Wicket Haul Leads J&K to Historic Ranji Semi-Final
item.description: Mohammad Nabi's remarkable 12-wicket performance propels Jammu and Kashmir to their first Ranji Trophy semi-final, defeating Madhya Pradesh.
